{"tid":794160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"童年懷舊-天龍八部","createTime":"2018-08-26T03:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T07:58:51.000Z","uid":5666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d3bfdd4a1652bc1c5bfb662e60039a968772f604","tid":794160,"uid":5666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:56:16.000Z","msg":"假日閒晃，驀地一道古典之音傳來，思緒由此回到十年前的8月。<br />\n那年8月，同樣躺在家，身旁一部電腦，不停重複播送著激昂的古箏之音，螢幕上顯示的仿佛回到了古代的樓蘭。鐵骨錚錚，戎馬生涯，只能以一句舊日情已逝作終。<br />\n<br />\n其實而家仲有無人玩天龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重新down返，已經無人再擺攤，只有一堆人不停解副本。想當年洛陽擺攤由西大街擺到東大街，仲多過所謂既女人街。可惜，好景不常，想玩返，但南ser變左鬼ser咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31de3743cd881f36e2fc190767fc14a77c722cae","tid":794160,"uid":71738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"南ser揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d82acc9fcf606ad6c5cc2ded35a7d306f9b90c2","tid":794160,"uid":5666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31de3743cd881f36e2fc190767fc14a77c722cae","tid":794160,"uid":71738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"南ser揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"而家無晒人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想玩返"},{"pid":"16be00e3479686a7d0adae25c2cf563d82540e9c","tid":794160,"uid":123042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T21:57:35.000Z","msg":"正常都去左玩陸服或者私服。"},{"pid":"be2b5b1bf81589941a207ed32e1c3f48f0ce5236","tid":794160,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T22:24:47.000Z","msg":"最終鍾過場景每個唔同派別果d 詩<br />\n<br />\n隻gama d 野真係值錢，咩貨倉抽中囉去賣左唔少金"},{"pid":"aca90526db5095e70eb1c1d126c3687e8f741dcf","tid":794160,"uid":192957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31de3743cd881f36e2fc190767fc14a77c722cae","tid":7